'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 12''' is the twelfth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 6|''Star Wars'' (1977) 6]] {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 7}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 7|The Sword in the Star! Stave 2: Witchworld!]]" {{C|Part 3}}

*"The Model Makers: The Real Stars of ''Star Wars''?" {{C|excerpt from the''[[Star Wars Official Collector's Edition]]''}}
*A competition to win one of twenty-four ''Star Wars'' bubble-bath packs. To enter, readers must answer six ''Star Wars'' related true-or-false questions.

